data.description: GORGEOUS 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom condo in the popular WesTown Condo complex in Arvada! Located at the base of the foothills, your future home offers an open floor plan between the Living Room, dining area, and eat-in Kitchen. The Kitchen features granite-slab countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and a center island with additional seating and storage. Relax in front of the fireplace in the living room while you watch the snow fall from the covered balcony. This unit has a split floor plan with a bed and bath on opposite sides for maximum privacy, as well as a Washer and Dryer in the unit. In addition to a security entrance, this condo is ideally located just minutes to Golden, convenient to Denver, and walking distance to numerous shops and transportation! Included: 3 breakfast bar stools, all kitchen appliances, washer and dryer, and all window coverings! Call now for a private showing!
